cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a generative model and uses the wake-sleep algorithm. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with machine learning and inference. It may also fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it deals with neural machine translation. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as it uses BLEU score as a metric, which is commonly used in computer vision tasks.
